These are packages which are supported for Raspberry Pi platforms.

locales-all is included within the image definition of pre-installed desktop
images to enable translations within gnome-initial-setup (e.g. the +raspi
images). See LP: #2118539 for more details.

 * locales-all

== non-free packages ==

Hardware support packages which are non-free, and so cannot be depended on by
metapackages which are in main, but nethertheless need to be supported. They
may be included into images by other means, e.g. by direct installation from
livecd-rootfs.

 * linux-firmware-raspi
